felt like three years.

299
00:32:32,750 --> 00:32:33,650
Jiu!

300
00:32:33,910 --> 00:32:34,860
Jiu!

301
00:32:36,170 --> 00:32:36,960
Jiu!

302
00:32:38,260 --> 00:32:39,340
Jiu!

303
00:32:39,910 --> 00:32:41,100
Brother Zhuo.

304
00:32:41,130 --> 00:32:42,070
Brother Zhuo, is that you?

305
00:32:42,070 --> 00:32:43,260
Brother Zhuo?

306
00:32:43,860 --> 00:32:45,240
So noisy.

307
00:32:48,010 --> 00:32:48,930
Look closely.

308
00:32:50,390 --> 00:32:52,210
I'm not your Jiu.

309
00:32:52,880 --> 00:32:54,490
I'm Li Lun.

310
00:32:55,680 --> 00:32:58,740
I will make sure you die knowing exactly who killed you.

311
00:32:58,910 --> 00:33:01,230
See with your last look

312
00:33:01,290 --> 00:33:03,100
who killed you.

313
00:34:09,800 --> 00:34:11,660
I hated this bow so much back then.

314
00:34:13,560 --> 00:34:14,489
I never imagined

315
00:34:14,870 --> 00:34:15,790
that one day

316
00:34:15,880 --> 00:34:17,330
I would risk my life

317
00:34:17,469 --> 00:34:19,199
fighting a demon to reclaim it.

318
00:34:34,250 --> 00:34:35,510
Thank you, Heng.

