♫I only hope the snow comes a bit later♫

325
00:35:12,080 --> 00:35:13,260
Mr. Zhuo!

326
00:35:54,000 --> 00:35:56,250
Don't you hurt Brother Zhuo!

327
00:36:20,070 --> 00:36:21,010
Brother Zhuo!

328
00:37:02,170 --> 00:37:04,020
Don't waste your effort.

329
00:37:04,720 --> 00:37:07,940
My inner core has been inside Bai Jiu's body for many days.

330
00:37:07,970 --> 00:37:10,070
My soul has already solidified,

331
00:37:10,110 --> 00:37:12,310
making it much stronger than Bai Jiu's.

332
00:37:12,750 --> 00:37:15,250
His soul is nothing but a weak ant

333
00:37:15,430 --> 00:37:17,500
compared to mine,

334
00:37:17,530 --> 00:37:19,390
which can be easily crushed by me.

335
00:37:21,370 --> 00:37:24,690
After staying for the last few hours,

336
00:37:25,440 --> 00:37:27,330
his soul

337
00:37:27,910 --> 00:37:30,570
will never come out again.

338
00:38:32,000 --> 00:38:33,810
I'm too timid.

339
00:38:34,210 --> 00:38:35,040
But

340
00:38:35,070 --> 00:38:37,800
whenever I hear the bells on your braids ringing,

341
00:38:39,060 --> 00:38:40,370
I know

342
00:38:40,510 --> 00:38:42,450
you're by my side.

343
00:38:43,750 --> 00:38:45,360
And I'll feel safe.

344
00:38:53,030 --> 00:38:54,310
Are you scared?

345
00:38:54,940 --> 00:38:56,410
With you

346
00:38:56,790 --> 00:38:58,910
and your powerful Cloud Light Sword here,

347
00:38:58,910 --> 00:39:00,390
I'm not that scared.

348
00:39:17,880 --> 00:39:19,230
I'm sure it will be fine.

349
00:40:05,820 --> 00:40:07,270
Mr. Zhuo!

350
00:40:10,360 --> 00:40:12,300
Your body can't take any more!

351
00:40:12,340 --> 00:40:14,800
Don't consume any more of your Bingyi blood!

352
00:40:34,620 --> 00:40:37,160
Give Jiu back to me!

353
00:42:14,940 --> 00:42:15,740
Zhuo!

354
00:42:19,170 --> 00:42:19,970
Li Lun!

355
00:42:30,580 --> 00:42:31,650
Mr. Zhuo.

356
00:42:36,450 --> 00:42:37,980
You're really hard to kill.

357
00:42:39,040 --> 00:42:41,300
You ultimately managed to escape death.

358
00:42:41,560 --> 00:42:43,740
How could I possibly die before you?

359
00:42:43,760 --> 00:42:45,370
Mr. Zhuo, wake up.

360
00:42:45,980 --> 00:42:48,040
I promise I won't argue with you anymore,

361
00:42:48,040 --> 00:42:48,760
okay?

362
00:42:49,130 --> 00:42:49,940
Mr. Zhuo.

363
00:42:50,230 --> 00:42:51,490
Zhao Yuanzhou,

364
00:42:52,020 --> 00:42:53,950
I'm actually very grateful to you.

365
00:42:56,070 --> 00:42:58,790
If it weren't for you bringing this kid to me,

366
00:42:59,190 --> 00:43:01,720
how could I have obtained such a perfect body,

367
00:43:01,810 --> 00:43:04,720
so well-matched to my pagoda ghost form?

368
00:43:06,760 --> 00:43:09,620
You've finally done something that makes me happy.

369
00:43:10,870 --> 00:43:13,070
You cooperated with Wen Zongyu

370
00:43:13,490 --> 00:43:15,670
just for this body, didn't you?

371
00:43:16,200 --> 00:43:17,580
You know very well

372
00:43:18,180 --> 00:43:21,040
that once you break free from Baize Goddess's seal,

373
00:43:21,270 --> 00:43:24,020
your true form will quickly wither and die.

374
00:43:25,430 --> 00:43:27,150
You do know me well.

375
00:43:28,850 --> 00:43:30,250
But if anyone's to blame,

376
00:43:31,860 --> 00:43:33,860
it's Wen Zongyu for being ruthless.

377
00:43:34,850 --> 00:43:37,370
He even sacrificed his disciple.

378
00:43:37,960 --> 00:43:39,790
I've always told you

379
00:43:39,870 --> 00:43:41,330
that humans, though weak,

380
00:43:41,370 --> 00:43:43,190
are far more vicious

381
00:43:43,490 --> 00:43:44,890
than powerful demons.

382
00:43:46,270 --> 00:43:47,630
You never believed me.

383
00:43:49,240 --> 00:43:51,840
Wen Zongyu could even sacrifice his disciple.

384
00:43:51,980 --> 00:43:53,780
You're not his family or friend.

385
00:43:53,790 --> 00:43:55,530
How could you not see this?

386
00:43:57,020 --> 00:43:58,640
Of course, I can see this.

387
00:44:00,480 --> 00:44:01,830
We are just

388
00:44:03,270 --> 00:44:05,530
using each other to get what we each want.

389
00:44:06,910 --> 00:44:07,810
Li Lun,

390
00:44:09,660 --> 00:44:11,660
do you know his true purpose?

391
00:44:14,890 --> 00:44:16,530
The people of the world,

392
00:44:17,620 --> 00:44:19,270
bustling with activity,

393
00:44:20,080 --> 00:44:21,810
are driven by greed and desire.

394
00:44:23,290 --> 00:44:25,300
Wen Zongyu covets power

395
00:44:25,640 --> 00:44:27,700
and wants to destroy the Baize Token,

396
00:44:27,850 --> 00:44:29,550
allowing the demons of the Wilderness

397
00:44:29,550 --> 00:44:31,470
to enter the mortal world and create chaos.

398
00:44:31,470 --> 00:44:32,950
By doing so, he hopes to

399
00:44:32,970 --> 00:44:36,500
recreate the glory of Chongwu Camp's dominance over the world.

400
00:44:37,390 --> 00:44:38,550
However,

401
00:44:38,790 --> 00:44:40,610
Wen Zongyu is too naive.

402
00:44:41,630 --> 00:44:43,270
The naive one is you,

403
00:44:44,100 --> 00:44:44,910
Li Lun.

404
00:44:45,510 --> 00:44:47,970
You've lived for tens of thousands of years,

405
00:44:48,750 --> 00:44:52,000
but you're not even as wise as a ten-year-old child in the mortal world.

406
00:44:52,000 --> 00:44:54,220
Wen Zongyu has been hunting monsters

407
00:44:54,460 --> 00:44:56,260
and secretly researching them,

408
00:44:56,580 --> 00:44:59,780
hoping to create demonized humans stronger than demons,

409
00:45:01,000 --> 00:45:03,750
to eliminate all the demons in the world

410
00:45:04,690 --> 00:45:07,420
and turn the Wilderness into a barren wasteland.

411
00:45:07,440 --> 00:45:09,730
This is his true purpose.

412
00:45:11,550 --> 00:45:12,950
What did you say?

413
00:45:13,120 --> 00:45:14,200
Eight years ago,

414
00:45:15,740 --> 00:45:18,620
in the mortal world, the little demons

415
00:45:19,950 --> 00:45:23,210
we saw being tortured in the dungeon

416
00:45:23,510 --> 00:45:26,750
were captured and imprisoned by Wen Zongyu's men.

417
00:45:27,330 --> 00:45:30,860
That was the very reason we turned against each other back then.

418
00:45:31,770 --> 00:45:33,010
But now,

419
00:45:34,480 --> 00:45:36,850
you are helping the very culprit.

420
00:45:38,790 --> 00:45:39,590
Li Lun,

421
00:45:40,370 --> 00:45:42,400
you once swore an oath with blood

422
00:45:43,520 --> 00:45:45,280
to protect the Wilderness.

423
00:45:49,270 --> 00:45:50,630
Have you forgotten?

424
00:45:52,360 --> 00:45:53,400
No, I haven't.

425
00:45:54,840 --> 00:45:56,200
You're lying to me.

426
00:45:58,080 --> 00:45:59,480
You're lying to me again.

427
00:46:00,160 --> 00:46:01,480
He's not lying.

428
00:46:03,200 --> 00:46:04,860
The one who's been lying to you

429
00:46:04,990 --> 00:46:06,710
is Wen Zongyu.

430
00:46:07,000 --> 00:46:08,330
If you don't believe it,

431
00:46:09,930 --> 00:46:12,660
go to the secret chamber in Chongwu Camp to check.

432
00:46:13,110 --> 00:46:15,060
There are the answers you want.

